# Trinidadian Doubles

Based on [Cooking with Ria](https://cookingwithria.com/2018/12/how-to-make-trinidad-doubles-detailed-recipe-instructions/), [Gaz Oakley](https://www.gazoakleychef.com/recipes/trinidadian-doubles/), and [TriniGourmet](https://www.trinigourmet.com/trinidad-doubles-recipe/)

